  <brief_title>Immediate Management of the Patient With Rupture : Open Versus Endovascular Repair</brief_title>
  <acronym>IMPROVE</acronym>
  <official_title>Can Emergency Endovascular Aneurysm Repair (eEVAR) Improve the Survival From Ruptured Abdominal Aortic Aneurysm?</official_title>
